RESOLUTION

HP has provided upgrades to resolve this vulnerability. 

For Installations Running Data Protector Express 4.x
=======================================
Microsoft Windows, Linux, Novell NetWare
 Install HP Data Protector Express 4.0 SP1 build 46537 or later, available here: 
ftp://dpxbits:dpxbits@...c.external.hp.com 
 
 
For Installations Running Data Protector Express Single Server Edition (SSE) 4.x
===========================================================
Microsoft Windows, Linux, Novell NetWare
 Install HP Data Protector Express 4.0 SP1 build 46537 or later. 
Note: Current HP Data Protector Express SSE customers must contact HP Services and Support directly for download instructions 


For Installations Running Data Protector Express 3.x
=======================================
Microsoft Windows, Linux, Novell NetWare 
 Install HP Data Protector Express 3.5 SP2 build 47065 or later, available here: 
ftp://dpxbits:dpxbits@...c.external.hp.com 
 

For Installations Running Data Protector Express Single Server Edition (SSE) 3.x
===========================================================
Microsoft Windows, Linux, Novell NetWare
 Install HP Data Protector Express 3.5 SP2 build 47065 or later. 
Note: Current HP Data Protector Express SSE customers must contact HP Services and Support directly for download instructions 
 

Note: For questions about upgrading Data Protector Express and Data Protector Express Single Server Edition, contact HP Services and Support. 

